tendo-xbox-tv -accessories&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv-accessories" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv-accessories</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T15:03:35-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T15:03:35-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年 PC 礼品指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星图形背景。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NKp7YtAgU_mcPIzB9I2SJBfnyLU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72825088/236830_PC_Gift_Guide_Art_CVirginia_ LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;对于那些花太多时间坐在笔记本电脑或台式电脑上的人来说，这是最好的科技礼物——无论是工作还是工作休闲。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T14:42:03-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T14:42:03-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 最受欢迎的 50 美元以下节日礼物</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/y3D6gomoRJ6DQHcOjUXr3cmWoC0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72860202/236830_UNDER_50_Gift_Guide_Artboards _CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;送礼不一定要耗费您所有的时间和金钱 - 我们已经收集了各种各样的廉价礼物来证明这一点。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T14:30:37-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T14:30:37-05:00</updated><title> 2023 年黑色星期五最佳游戏优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;靠在 PlayStation 5 主机上的白色 DualSense 控制器的特写。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/pDnPcY3wRNsQnoSMqIgo_45cOkU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72893119/vpavic_4261_20201023_0028 .0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Vjeran Pavic / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;SLvuFB&quot;>;现在是储备游戏和游戏配件的最佳时机 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/23939216/black-friday-guide-cyber-monday-tech-gadgets-2023&quot;>;黑色星期五&lt;/a>;，而今年，我们看到今年发布的一些最大的游戏有相当大的折扣 —需要我提醒您的是，这一年里充斥着许多优秀的游戏。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;csoMnq&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem -component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;pbjdk6&quot;>;虽然并非今年所有最热门的游戏都获得大幅折扣，但诸如 &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BPMTJJ6D?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;最终幻想 XVI&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Resident-Evil-4-Xbox-X-PlayStation/dp/B0BJTSN9ZC?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em >;生化危机 4&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 重制版。当谈到稍旧的游戏时，很多，比如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=nOD%2FrLJHOac&amp;amp;mid=24348&amp;amp;u1=verge&amp;amp;murl=https%3A%2F %2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fvideo-games%2Fproducts%2Fdoom-eternal---playstation-4%2F171397.html&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;毁灭永恒&lt;/em>;&lt; /a>;，只需微薄的价格即可获得，因此这是一个囤积几个月甚至几年前您可能错过的版本的好时机。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;reYicY&quot;>;至于游戏配件和外围设备、黑色星期五和网络星期一总是会提供大量有价值的折扣，例如...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971228/black-friday-2023-gaming -game-deals-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23971228/black-friday-2023-gaming-game-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23971228/black-friday-2023-gaming-game-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T14:18:40-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T14:18:40-05:00</updated><title> Bard 现在可以为您观看 YouTube 视频</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示巴德徽标以及 Gmail、云端硬盘、文档和其他应用程序的图形&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/F_HVrPCg69HxznMUIQRHq7h_1kQ=/129x0:1071x628/1310x873/ cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72893066/google_bard_extensions.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Bard 继续以越来越有用的方式利用 Google 的服务和平台群。&lt;/em>; |图片：Google&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;bbWSMZ&quot;>;Bard，Google 的 AI 聊天机器人，拥有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/19/23878999/google -bard-ai-chatbot-gmail-docs-drive-extensions&quot;>;在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/3/21/23650472/google之后，逐渐变得更加有用&lt;/a>; -bard-ai-chatbot-hands-on-test&quot;>;乏善可陈的介绍&lt;/a>;。现在，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.androidauthority.com/google-bard-youtube-understanding-3388018/&quot;>;正如 Android Authority 所指出的，&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;机器人的 YouTube 集成&lt;a href=&quot;https://bard.google.com/updates&quot;>;正在进行便捷升级&lt;/a>;，因此它可以分析各个视频，为您显示具体信息（例如要点或食谱成分），而无需按玩。这可能是一个非常有用的工具，但可能会给创作者带来更多关于生成人工智能的担忧。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;BoOWJk&quot;>;为了尝试一下，我向巴德打开了一个我经常参考的 YouTube 视频以获取精神指导：&lt; a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iCNVvPB6zVI&quot;>;美国测试厨房的浓缩咖啡马提尼配方&lt;/a>;。说真的，这真的很好。我经常发现自己在厨房里，鸡尾酒调酒器里有一半的原料，试图记住我有多少本笃会......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023 /11/22/23972636/bard-youtube-extension-update-search-video-content&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972636/bard-youtube-extension-update-search-video-content" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972636/bard-youtube-extension-update-search-video-content</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T14:01:33-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T14:01:33-05:00</updated><title>福特缩减了密歇根州的电动汽车电池工厂计划</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;F-150 Lightning 正面的福特标志&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lkF78tk2ouw4ezDZzMUrDKzJPsA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72892990/ahawkins_220504_5202_0010.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;全电动 F-150 Lightning 的特写。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Andrew Hawkins / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;czzFLD&quot;>;福特宣布，由于客户购买电动汽车的需求降温以及劳动力成本上升，它将削减即将建成的电动汽车电池工厂的产能。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://media.ford.com/content/fordmedia/fna/us/en/news/2023/11/21/blue-oval-battery-park-michigan-update.html&quot;>;汽车制造商表示&lt;/a>;将把原来建造密歇根工厂的 35 亿美元计划投资减少到 20 亿美元左右，现在预计只雇用 1,700 名工人，而不是 2,500 名。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;F39rAq&quot;>;福特&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/2/11/23595909/ford-battery-plant-michigan-evs&quot;>;最初宣布&lt;/a>;于二月份合作建设雄心勃勃的密歇根电池工厂与中国宁德时代新能源科技有限公司（CATL）合作，该公司生产 LFP（磷酸铁锂）电池。该工厂现在每年仅生产约 20 吉瓦时的电池，产量减少约 43%。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;bcP7Sg&quot;>;为了让电动汽车有资格获得高达 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/4/20/23691597/ev-tax-credit-eligible-vehicles-battery-irs-china&quot;>;7,500 美元...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972680/ford-michigan-ev-battery-plant-reduction-plans&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972680/ford-michigan-ev-battery-plant-reduction-plans" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972680/ford-michigan-ev-battery-plant-reduction-plans</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T13:59:32-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T13:59:32-05:00</updated><title> Max、Paramount Plus、Hulu 等平台的最佳黑色星期五流媒体优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;绿色和白色背景上的 Hulu 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3j-f3ef4ipJwlDcnjluNSqJnvu0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72891666/acastro_STK061_hulu_04.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;一年支持广告的 Hulu 现在不到 12 美元。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge &lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Up5UhG&quot;>;如果感觉像每个流媒体服务&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23901586/streaming-service -prices-netflix-disney-hulu-peacock-max&quot;>;今年价格上涨&lt;/a>;，可能是因为大多数都涨价了。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/18/23922319/netflix-q3-earnings-2023-price-hike-increase-basic-premium&quot;>;Netflix&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/25/23931577/apple-tv-plus-news-arcade-one-subscription-price-increase&quot;>;Apple TV Plus&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/3/23901448/discovery-plus-price-increase-monthly-cost&quot;>;Discovery Plus&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/2023/8/9/23826500/disney-plus-hulu-no-ads-plan-price-increases&quot;>;Disney Plus&lt;/a>; 只是最近的几个例子，但仍有方法以应对价格上涨。毕竟，黑色星期五带来了各种各样的优惠，包括节省每月流媒体账单的方法。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;VJkz6i&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您现在可以购买的最佳早期黑色星期五科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday- tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday -gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;7hzi4e&quot;>;事实上，一些流媒体服务正在提供抵消了最近价格上涨的交易——至少暂时是这样。例如，Paramount Plus 可能&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/22/23733505/paramount-plus-showtime-price-increase&quot;>;将其最便宜计划的价格提高到每月 5.99 美元&lt;/a>;，但目前起价仅为 1.99 美元。更好的是，新订阅者和回访订阅者都有资格享受这笔交易，这是真正的罕见......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black- friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black-friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black-friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T13:32:30-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T13:32:30-05:00</updated><title>黑色星期五 100 美元以下最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一只手举起 Kindle Paperwhite&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VRNp93gtsOhpHG4GX23T2Lf60DQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72892831/cgartenberg_211020_4803_0003.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Kindle Paperwhite 是一款很受欢迎的礼物，当您购买几乎相同的儿童友好型号时，它的价格不到 100 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chaim Gartenberg / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Xpmerm&quot;>;这是一年中最美好的时光？噗，更像是最贵的。礼物、旅行、装饰品、聚会、美味佳肴……所有这些加起来可以让你的钱包省不少钱。这就是为什么我们努力以各种方式帮助您节省费用，从 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget &quot;>;针对&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21587765/black-friday-cyber-monday-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;>;产品制定经济实惠的礼品指南&lt;/a>;寻找交易的技巧&lt;/a>;。现在，我们在下面汇总了 100 美元以下的最佳黑色星期五优惠 — 其中许多是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas -unique-tech-gadgets&quot;>;我们的礼品指南中的特色内容&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;k8loXn&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas -2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 25 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23874403/tech-gifts-under-25-best-cheap -ideas-stocking-stuffers-2023-budget&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;zqcCCP&quot;>;我们发现了一系列打折的小玩意和商品，可用于很棒的礼物，来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Lavender-Bloom-bundle-TP-Link-Smart/dp/B0CL8HJ3HD?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; 目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Fitbit-Exercise-Equipment-6-Months-Membership/dp/B0CC62ZG1M?tag=theverge02-20&quot; 相关=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fitbit Charge 6&lt;/a>; 到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Fujifilm-Instax-Mini-Instant-Camera/dp/B0BWP15J1P? tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fujifilm Instax Mini 12&lt;/a>; 甚至一对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-AirPods -Charging-Latest-Model/dp/B07PXGQC1Q?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;AirPods&lt;/a>;。不过，还有一些优惠可以帮助您节省其他费用，例如换色 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CCYSDP2V?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener “ target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;节日智能灯串...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech -deals-under-100-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T12:47:52-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T12:47:52-05:00</updated><title> WiiM Amp 是一款具有 Mac Mini 风格的流媒体接收器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;从四分之三角度拍摄的 WiiM 放大器图片。它是灰色的，形状大致像 Mac Mini，右前方有一个大旋钮，中间有一个播放按钮。左侧一条深灰色的铅笔粗线几乎延伸到左角。该线左端上方有一个紫色电源 LED，在其右侧上方，有 6 个圆形 LED 用来指示音量——左边 4 个是亮起来，最右边的稍微变暗。另外两个是黑暗的。” src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yVVW1Nt7qaPgSnDh6XOC1fBOiio=/160x0:1890x1153/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72892652/WiiM_Amp___Lifestyle_4.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;售价 299 美元的 WiiM Amp 具有无源立体声扬声器输出和大量流媒体支持。&lt;/em>; |图片：Linkplay Technology&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;wTvSp7&quot;>;Linkplay Technology 今天宣布了其产品阵容的新成员：&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CGCLXH4H ?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;WiiM 放大器&lt;/a>;。这款售价 299 美元的设备作为接收器具有明显的复古焦点，甚至比 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/8/23822610/wiim-pro-plus-streamer-multiroom -audio-streaming-release-date&quot;>;WiiM Pro Plus&lt;/a>;，该公司于今年早些时候推出，得益于物理输出，可以让您直接输出到一组老式无源立体声扬声器。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;10DvDX&quot;>;WiiM Amp 现在是该公司最昂贵的流媒体盒，但它有可能为合适的人赢得它。得益于丰富的流媒体标准支持以及适合自带扬声器人群的独特输出集，它比大多数紧凑型 AirPlay 2 接收器更加通用。这可能只占人口的一小部分，但像这样的无线接收器并不多……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/ 11/22/23972352/wiim-amp-airplay-2-chromecast-wireless-receiver-vintage-hi-fi&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972352/wiim-amp-airplay-2-chromecast-wireless-receiver-vintage-hi-fi" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972352/wiim-amp-airplay-2-chromecast-wireless-receiver-vintage-hi-fi</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry></feed>